manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.

playstore_details.title: Bitcoin Wallet by SpectroCoin
playstore_details.description:
Buy, store, exchange and spend your crypto or traditional currencies, anytime, anywhere. In addition to Bitcoin, our wallet app features support for a variety of cryptocurrencies and stablecoins. With SpectroCoin Android app, you can take full advantage of your Bitcoin (BTC), Ethereum (ETH), Tether (USDT), NEM (XEM), Banker (BNK), and DASH. Our digital wallets provide more than 20 methods for depositing and withdrawing digital assets, including linked cards and bank transfers. The app also offers support for traditional fiat currencies such as EUR, USD, and GBP, to name a few.

SpectroCoin mobile wallet is designed to be functional, safe and easy to navigate on your Android devices. Get real-time information about your account balance and transaction history, keep track of the value of your digital assets, and stay informed with our updates and features.

During our six years in the crypto scene, what has driven us is the goal of offering the best possible cryptocurrency solutions to our customers. Join more than one million people in over 150 countries who trust SpectroCoin every day.

ENHANCED SECURITY 

We respect your privacy and collect only necessary data, which is processed and stored in accordance with applicable laws. We give you great control, so you can always manage and update your SpectroCoin account easily. As with so many things, it is a matter of balancing security and convenience. A safe environment, in which you can exchange cryptocurrency and make borderless payments, requires industry-leading safety standards, including multi-stage account verification, advanced authentication methods, and bank-level security. 

SUPPORT 24/7

Our customers are our highest priority, so if you are having any issues, send us an email at helpdesk@spectrocoin.com. Alternatively, you can contact our 24/7 support via the “Live Chat” option available on our website.

Simply download the Bitcoin Wallet by SpectroCoin and manage your cryptocurrencies on-the-go!
